  ('dietitian-moex-11337', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', 'IDDM病人運動前血糖在180~200 mg/dL間，預計執行一緩和的運動，時間約為 40 分鐘，則此病人在運動前該如 何？ 不需要額外補充任何食物    建議補充含15公克醣的食物 建議補充含蛋白質食物    建議額外補充10公克油脂', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c35cacfa49d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11338', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於type1糖尿病之敘述，何者不正確？ 無法以口服降血糖藥控制血糖  患者通常體重正常或略輕 需嚴格限制醣類之攝取至總熱量之40﹪  因胰臟β細胞受到破壞而致', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c35cacfa49d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11339', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關胰島素之敘述，何者為非？ 胰島素需採注射方式，才可發生作用  胰島素劑量過高時，會因血糖過低休克 當患者因發燒而減少進食量時，應降低胰島素之劑量  耐力運動可減少胰島素之需要量', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c35cacfa49d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
